Author: fuck_you_get_pumped
Text: seeing her arms in pictures really made me feel for her. i haven't suffered what she did, but i know the kind of hell she mentioned. anyone else feeling that way, feel free to message me if you want. i'm a good listener and never judge. also, know that it will get better if you are patient. i always thought i'd be dead before twenty. now i'm 23 and actually happy sometimes. please be willing to try anything but suicide. just in case it might work.
